    <defName>GorStrangeRunt</defName>
    <title>strange gor</title>
    <titleShort>strange</titleShort>
    <baseDesc>[PAWN_nameDef] was born as a mutant. Abandoned like so many other mutants [PAWN_pronoun] was left to fend for [PAWN_possessive] life and joined a passing gor herd. [PAWN_pronoun] was a tad stranger than the rest, for the touch of chaos might linger in [PAWN_possessive] mind.</baseDesc>
